  "prompt": "Is there any app that gives free data everyday in Grameenphone?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, Grameenphone, a leading telecommunications provider in Bangladesh, occasionally offers promotional packages and apps that provide free data to its users. One such example was the **\"MyGP\" app**, which sometimes includes rewards or free data for daily usage or specific activities.\n\nHowever, whether you get **free data every day** depends on ongoing promotions, which can vary. Grameenphone often runs campaigns where users can earn free data by participating in quizzes, watching ads, or completing certain tasks through their app or other platforms.\n\nHere\u2019s what you can do:\n1. **Download the MyGP app**: Check for any ongoing offers or rewards.\n2. **Subscribe to GP's official channels**: Follow their social media pages or subscribe to their notifications for updates on free data promotions.\n3. **Check balance codes**: Use USSD codes like *566# to see if any free data is available.\n\nAlways verify the terms and conditions of any offer, as free data may come with restrictions (e.g., limited validity or usage caps). If there\u2019s a specific app or promotion you\u2019re looking for, it\u2019s best to contact Grameenphone's customer care for the latest information.",
